          "cond": { "not": { "flag": "garden_acoustics_done" } },
          "text": "The stone table under the study window. Standing at the window above, Gary can hear the garden — but only when the wind drops. A whole conversation, delivered in halves. That's how you overhear enough to be wrong.",
